title: ImTOO iPhone Photo Transfer v 1.1.4.20131114 Multilanguage-TeamG
description:
Simplify Your iPhone Photos Transfer Workflow
Customize your iPhone digital photos workflow with new photo management capabilities with ImTOO iPhone Photo Transfer. Use thumbnail and image preview to quickly select your photos and transfer to computer immediately. Moreover, you are also able to transfer videos shot by iPhone to computer and upload to websites for sharing with friends and family, pass wanted picture from your computer to iPhone for enjoying everywhere and anytime, connect multiple iPhone simultaneously to share images between them without limitation.

Do More with Advanced and Easy Album-managing Functions
ImTOO offers the best solution to manage, organize and edit photo albums for iPhone at the same time. You can establish photo albums as wish, select photos and move into or move out of the album, set one specified photo as the cover for the album.
